{
  "stem": "2118.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the letter said, the card said, she was sent to a town in Germany which was fictitious.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The town existed, but was fictitious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Augsburg, the city of Augsburg-- but they never went to Augsburg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They never went more than 20 miles behind lodge, where they were killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he took us with a train-- they put us on a train and they sent us into Germany, supposedly to the same factory with the Poles to work in Cieszanow.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The day or two days before, the factory-- we were sent out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The SS came and took over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was already a different story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Before, you could still talk to a German [? or ?] [? think-- ?] But we still didn't realize what it was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they put us on a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we traveled to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It took us maybe four days at least.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The train consisted of a big cattle wagon, which was divided in three parts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the two sides were people from-- us, the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in the middle was divided, was a soldier sitting there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Or every night or some nights, the soldier went down, and they locked the wagons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were given a little water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And if we were stopped someplace on the sidewalk, on a sideline, which was plenty, they did allow us to go down and do toilet or things like this.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we arrived in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't remember the exact date.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But it was late in August or very beginning of September.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "A couple days before we arrived, they-- Buchenwald had a factory working for the German armament.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I think the name was Gustloff-- the Gustloff Werke.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they bombed-- the Americans bombed the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the line that they-- line got burned out.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
